Modify from improved_trajectory_release, work by Cordelia Group on ICCV13.
The modification is to take input as frame pattern instead of video file.
The frames can be any image type.

E.g.,

> ./release/m_DenseTrackStab ./test_sequences/frames/frm_%06d.png > out.features
> ./release/m_DenseTrackStab ./test_sequences/frames/frm_%06d.jpg > out.features